featured.text: Whale experts found Tag, Notch, Baby alive.
Their names are Tag, Notch, and Baby.
After their release, Tag, Notch, and Baby were never seen again.
The three whales Tag, Notch, and Baby were rescued because (A) younger whales have a greater chance of survival than the others.

definition.en_def: A V-shaped cut or indentation in an object, often used for marking or fitting.
definition.example: He made a notch in the wood to mark where to cut.
